      "name": "Özellikler",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "baseInfo",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Name",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Consecrated Flying Serpent</p>"
                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Type",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Mystical Beasts</p>"
                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>A reptile that was warped and transformed by its consumption of the body of a mighty life-form. During combat, it will enter the powerful Phagocytic form. Some of its attacks will unleash Phagocytic Energy Blocks. <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Use the corresponding elemental attacks to destroy these Energy Blocks</span> to absorb the power within them, which can then be unleashed when attacking the Consecrated Flying Serpent, dealing significant DMG and paralyzing the creature temporarily.</p>"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
